      <description/>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 May 2026 15:43:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <content:encoded> &lt;b&gt;▲헤럴드경제&lt;/b&gt;▷강원취재본부장 함영훈&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</content:encoded>
